Tridrones are [[modron]]s shaped like inverted pyramids, and can perform up to three tasks at a time. They have three arms and six spindly legs.

Like all [[modron]]s, {{!!title}}s have [[truesight]] out to 120 feet and can't be compelled to act in a manner contrary to their nature or their instructions.